:

1. *Noge* su mi se umorile od hodanja. (My legs got tired from walking.)
2. Moram da počnem da vežbam *noge*. (I need to start exercising my legs.)
3. Imala je lepu obuću na *noge*. (She had nice shoes on her feet.)
4. On je imao dugačke *noge*. (He had long legs.)
5. Putovali smo bez obuće na *noge*. (We traveled without shoes on our feet.)